---
title: Chicken and Mushroom Noodles				 with chilli flakes and scallion garnish
description: These vibrant chicken and mushroom noodles are creamy with just a bit of a kick. The scallion topping adds both a pop of colour and a kick of flavour to an already delicious dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R15_W24_IE_IEQCLC15151-2_Main_high-5560061d.jpg
